Delibird (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0224: Octillery
Pokémon
#0226: Mantine →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Delibird (TCG Pocket).

Delibird has been featured on 13 different cards since it debuted in the Neo Revelation expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Delibird cards are normally Water-type or Colorless-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Delibird

Delibird
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
